# This file is typically a symlink, e.g. to
#   ${PDK_ROOT}/sky130A/libs.tech/magic/sky130A.magicrc
# magic will crash if your rc file has bogus file paths (or something else is
# wrong) - this can happen if you point to the magicrc file in the FOSS Sky130
# libraries and, for example, don't have PDK_ROOT set.
source sky130A.magicrc
